Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 拓人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和子好像请假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君也没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人同学有什么消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君明知可能会死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是驯化了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:00:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津名志同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…到！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答刚才的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我没听课
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课东张西望也要适可而止哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到王之柱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh复活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团 第2队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放逐时代代表海德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团总会 现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如各位所知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚王之柱贯穿了本岛的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:04:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤须方驯化了素体Samekh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招致这种事态的第3队九重葛责任重大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是一直处于可以驯化的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧发生在昨晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么就成了我们九重葛的责任？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是他现在的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据遗留记录
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Samekh过去所有的驾驭者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在使王之柱出现后再也没有醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说是形同死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者已经断了气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 有必要确认进藤须方的当前状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若Samekh的驾驭者觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绮罗星十字团也必须考虑相应对策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若与之为敌会很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 也算是沉醉的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就让九重葛来负责吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要负责到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟他打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 尽情展现你拿手的游泳本领吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是对他们抱有期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天社团活动休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 只是听到声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是单人戏剧的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯咖啡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子似乎从天亮前就在海湾独自净身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在祈祷须方君能醒过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好友三人组之一待在这里没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心须方 也担心和子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然担心…可是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 现在我还能做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不是三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是两人和一人吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得已经迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕你已无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是他们俩的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他们认识的时间更长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们背负着无法想像的沉重命运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能获得幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我无法想象他们真正获得幸福的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们所背负的问题都无法解决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 自从你来到岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你和他们俩和睦相处三人同行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎的 觉得让他们幸福的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你们好友三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那开心的笑容之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始有了这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来干大事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 讴歌青春对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是来对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你们让我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的救命恩人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子似乎很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有拓人这样的人出现在岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的素体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全部破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能为他们俩做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是陪在身边也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望朋友陪在身边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都会有不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他们来说你就是这种朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他们不这么希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的灵魂也一定在渴求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两人都很笨拙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是孤岛长大的乡下人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是和子的祖母吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tau的印记是几时继承的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一年前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子在海湾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 因为想见和子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启 电气柩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现在这里就说明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化「柱」后 还一息尚存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的重赛 银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你…须方他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要清除外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我们的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上的遗迹全部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这些人偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游弋吧 美人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下潜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸裂 Tau银河光线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会又失控吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿成这样想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零时空间里 须方醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去大屋找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得马上去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王宣布让出王位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王最初就打算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把王位让给带来青色血液的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是萨姆拒绝接受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王 我只想要您的银河之船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘坐它 迈上驶往璀璨银河的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要什么王位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无意拥有什么国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到鱼妹妹的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有了干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王则说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有言在先 会给你任何想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦无意违背诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那艘银河之船让于你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼刺客萨姆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心听好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想开动那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:19:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你须将恋爱中少女的鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一滴不剩 注入它的引擎中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 必须杀死恋爱中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则无法开动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在起它是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜啊 这糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的冒险仍在继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤须方大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为恭迎您加入我们绮罗星十字团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特此前来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第一队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王之座 为你空缺已久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有意识呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让银河美少年靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.53,0:21:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算用王之柱 撤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复平时的须方了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你打的我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 想找死吗
